{"parentUuid":"0a3080f3-a796-47fa-80b8-da2ce9e67018","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/a111111/code/ai-video-collection","sessionId":"4bf88f6e-b607-435b-a8a6-907dc95cfbd4","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"fix/remove-nav-home-effects","message":{"content":[{"text":"你是在问 Claude Code 中如何授权/允许所有操作权限吗？\n\nClaude Code 有几种方式来管理权限：\n\n**1. 会话内快捷操作**\n- 当工具调用弹出权限确认时，可以选择：\n  - `Allow once` — 允许一次\n  - `Allow always` — 对该类操作永久允许（写入 `.claude/settings.json`）\n\n**2. 命令行参数**\n- `claude --dangerously-skip-permissions` — 跳过所有权限检查（需要先接受风险提示）\n\n**3. 配置文件 `.claude/settings.json`**\n- 在 `allowedTools` 中添加工具名来永久允许特定工具，例如：\n  ```json\n  {\n    \"allowedTools\": [\"Bash\", \"Edit\", \"Write\", \"Glob\", \"Grep\", \"Read\"]\n  }\n  ```\n\n**4. 本项目的 CLAUDE.md 约定**\n- 根据你的全局规则，当你对某个计划说\"同意\"时，即代表该任务所有操作权限均已授权，无需再次询问。\n\n---\n\n你想要的是哪种场景？是想对当前会话中的某个具体任务授权，还是想全局配置权限？","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_01LWX3TMhqHaVWiNBeAU6n4y","model":"claude-opus-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":26433,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":422,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":26433,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"3fa73217-4dbf-494b-849b-803767ce19ff","timestamp":"2026-03-02T09:43:22.687Z"}
